Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想暂时休学一段时间
